@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ==========================================
### Upload Flow (SAS two-step)
### ==========================================

### Step 1: Request Upload URL
# @name requestUpload
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/files/SUBMISSION/1/request-upload HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "originalName": "test-document.pdf",
    "mimeType": "application/pdf"
}


### Step 2: Upload file directly to Azure
PUT {{requestUpload.response.body.uploadUrl}} HTTP/1.1
x-ms-blob-type: BlockBlob
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./test-files/test-document.pdf


### Step 3: Confirm Upload
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/files/SUBMISSION/1/confirm-upload HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "uuid": "{{requestUpload.response.body.uuid}}",
    "originalName": "test-document.pdf",
    "mimeType": "application/pdf",
    "sizeBytes": 12345
}


### ==========================================
### Upload Flow (with submission file type)
### ==========================================

### Step 1: Request Upload URL (RECOGNITION)
# @name requestUploadRecognition
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/files/SUBMISSION/1/request-upload HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "originalName": "recognition-cert.pdf",
    "mimeType": "application/pdf",
    "submissionFileType": "RECOGNITION"
}


### Step 2: Upload file directly to Azure
PUT {{requestUploadRecognition.response.body.uploadUrl}} HTTP/1.1
x-ms-blob-type: BlockBlob
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./test-files/test-document.pdf


### Step 3: Confirm Upload (RECOGNITION)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/files/SUBMISSION/1/confirm-upload HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "uuid": "{{requestUploadRecognition.response.body.uuid}}",
    "originalName": "recognition-cert.pdf",
    "mimeType": "application/pdf",
    "sizeBytes": 12345,
    "submissionFileType": "RECOGNITION"
}


### ==========================================
### Query & Access
### ==========================================

### Get Files - Submission (all active)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/SUBMISSION/1 HTTP/1.1


### Get Files - Submission (filter by status)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/SUBMISSION/1?status=ACTIVE HTTP/1.1


### Get Files - Submission (filter by submission file type)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/SUBMISSION/1?submissionFileType=ATTACHMENT HTTP/1.1


### Get Files - Submission (filter recognition files)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/SUBMISSION/1?submissionFileType=RECOGNITION HTTP/1.1


### Preview File (replace UUID with actual value)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/preview HTTP/1.1


### Download File (replace UUID with actual value)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/download HTTP/1.1


### Delete File (replace UUID with actual value)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/files/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000 HTTP/1.1
